title: trillian_Chatting_Tool-v3 Pro 3.1.9.0
description:
Trillian Pro 3.1.9.0
Here&#039;s the steps.

1. Extract "Trillian Pro 3.1.9.0.rar" and "Crack.rar"
2. Install Trillian 3.1.9.0
3. After installation run Trillian.
4. When asked to choose between basic and pro just choose basic.
5. Let it load up then exit Trillian.
6. After exiting Trillian go to the Trillian installation directory (Default is C:Program FilesTrillian)
7. Go to the Trillian Pro 3.1.9.0 Folder you downloaded then extract "Crack.rar".
8. After you&#039;ve extracted "Crack.rar" copy "trillian.exe" into the installation directory.
9. When prompted to overwrite "trillian.exe" just say yes and overwrite it.
10. Run the program.
11. Enjoy.

For those who already have Trillian installed and have updated.

1. Extract "Crack.rar"
2. Open up the Trillian installation directory (Default is C:Program FilesTrillian)
3. Go to the Trillian 3.1.9.0 Folder and copy the cracked trillian.exe into the installation directory.
4. Enjoy.
